00029  SUBROUTINE VtkPlane
00030 
00031 ! Common Variables
00032  USE Domain,      ONLY : NX, NY, xl, xu, yl, yu
00033  USE FluidParams, ONLY : p, rho, u
00034  USE MPI
00035  IMPLICIT NONE
00036 
00037 ! Required functions
00038  CHARACTER(12) :: filer
00039 
00040 ! Local Variables
00041  INTEGER :: i, j
00042  INTEGER :: IO_ERR, MPI_ERR
00043  CHARACTER(12) :: filer1
00044  CHARACTER(16) :: fmtd1, fmtd3
00045  CHARACTER(20) :: filer2
00046 
00047 
00048 ! Set output files formats and names
00049  fmtd1 = '(1(ES21.11E3))'
00050  fmtd3 = '(3(ES21.11E3))'
00051  filer1 = filer()
00052  filer2 = "DATA"//filer1(1:12)//".vtk"
00053 
00054  OPEN(UNIT = 12, FILE = filer2, STATUS = "NEW", POSITION = "APPEND", &
00055       IOSTAT = IO_ERR)
00056  IF ( IO_ERR == 0 ) THEN
00057    WRITE(12,'(A)')"# vtk DataFile Version 2.0"
00058    WRITE(12,'(A)')"MP-LABS v1.0"
00059    WRITE(12,'(A)')"ASCII"
00060    WRITE(12,*)
00061    WRITE(12,'(A)')"DATASET STRUCTURED_POINTS"
00062    WRITE(12,*)"DIMENSIONS",NX,NY,1
00063    WRITE(12,*)"ORIGIN",xl,yl,1
00064    WRITE(12,*)"SPACING",1,1,1
00065    WRITE(12,*)
00066    WRITE(12,*)"POINT_DATA",NX*NY
00067    WRITE(12,*)
00068    WRITE(12,'(A)')"SCALARS Density double"
00069    WRITE(12,'(A)')"LOOKUP_TABLE default"
00070    DO j = yl, yu
00071        DO i = xl, xu
00072           WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd1)rho(i,j)
00073        END DO
00074    END DO
00075    WRITE(12,*)
00076    WRITE(12,'(A)')"SCALARS Pressure double"
00077    WRITE(12,'(A)')"LOOKUP_TABLE default"
00078    DO j = yl, yu
00079        DO i = xl, xu
00080           WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd1)p(i,j)
00081        END DO
00082    END DO
00083    WRITE(12,*)
00084    WRITE(12,'(A)')"VECTORS Velocity double"
00085    DO j = yl, yu
00086        DO i = xl, xu
00087          WRITE(UNIT = 12,FMT = fmtd3)u(i,j,1),u(i,j,2),0.D0
00088       END DO
00089    END DO
00090    CLOSE(UNIT = 12)
00091  ELSE
00092    CALL MemAlloc(2)
00093    CALL MPI_FINALIZE(MPI_ERR)
00094    STOP "Error: Unable to open output vtk file."
00095  END IF
00096 
00097  RETURN
00098  END SUBROUTINE VtkPlane
